                            </p>
                        </article>

                         <!-- card 2 -->
                         <article class="testimonial_card swiper-slide">
                            <img src="https://publika.ge/app/uploads/2020/03/publika.ge-5--1-1-768x768.jpg" alt="profile-pic" class="testimonial_img">
